        {
            "id": "f6749ebe819340b387563",
            "questionText": "A rower applies a constant forward force of $!$350 \\text{ N}$!$ to propel a boat. The total mass of the boat and rower is $!$120 \\text{ kg}$!$. The boat experiences water resistance of $!$180 \\text{ N}$!$ and air resistance of $!$70 \\text{ N}$!$. Calculate the boat\\'s acceleration.",
            "imageText": "",
            "steps": [
                {
                    "id": "4166cc0922964fffad7ca",
                    "stepText": "Let's start by finding the net force acting on the boat. Consider the forward force provided by the rower opposed by the water and air resistances. Calculate the net force by subtracting the total resistive force from the applied force.",
                    "stepText2": "",
                    "stepImage": "",
                    "stepSolveAnswer": [
                        "100"
                    ],
                    "stepSolveAnswerUnits": "N",
                    "stepConcepts": [
                        "3e20303c-d807-4753-b313-0259b2682a2e"
                    ],
                    "options": []
                },
                {
                    "id": "d2a28b1784424d2eab3a2",
                    "stepText": "Great, now that we have the net force, we need to identify the correct formula that relates net force, mass, and acceleration. Which one of the following formulas should be used in this situation?",
                    "stepText2": "",
                    "stepImage": "",
                    "stepSolveAnswer": [
                        ""
                    ],
                    "stepSolveAnswerUnits": "",
                    "stepConcepts": [
                        "8e5c203a-4499-44a1-a7ba-01198c1c2525",
                        "356d493b-02b5-4b95-b7b5-f34b9ec99aa1"
                    ],
                    "options": [
                        {
                            "optionText": "$!$F = ma$!$",
                            "optionImage": "",
                            "isCorrect": true
                        },
                        {
                            "optionText": "$!$F = m + a$!$",
                            "optionImage": "",
                            "isCorrect": false
                        },
                        {
                            "optionText": "$!$a = Fm$!$",
                            "optionImage": "",
                            "isCorrect": false
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "id": "45511555d94d4663a0439",
